    "The interested reader is referred to [18].Using the relative importance of keywords, we can, for example, see when certain terms are searched for most.",
    "Below is an example for the query \"PendSV\", which was a concept introduced approximately halfway through the course, and on which a lab was based (the large spike corresponds exactly to the lab date).",
    "By classifying queries by the level in the Bloom's Taxonomy, we can derive further insights.",
    "For instance, by analyzing the relative percentage of queries in each Bloom's level over time, we can see some interested trends emerge.",
